Title: Cockroaches
Plot: The team investigates an underground mob.  Warrick ends up becoming the prime suspect in a murder that's related to the mob, and his addiction to pills starts to have a significant impact on his job as a CSI.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Rick Hoffman, Beth Broderick, John Capodice, Rebecca Budig, Conor O'Farrell, Dennis Christopher, Archie Kao, David Berman
